      • parse

        public java_cup.runtime.Symbol parse()
                              throws java.lang.Exception
        After we parse as usual, the AST may contain reftype_or_expr nodes wrapped in expressions. These are the _only_ reftype_or_expr expressions in the AST at this point, although there may be reftype_or_expr types, qualifiers, etc. Here, we make a visitor pass over the AST to unwrap these reftype_or_expr nodes and convert them to (possibly reftype_or_expr) expressions. This pass is done after parsing to avoid having to convert expressions into types.
        Overrides:
        parse in class java_cup.runtime.lr_parser
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
